Subject: [PATCH 1/2] feat: hide zero-value rows with toggle button across all
 budget views

Rows where all numeric columns are zero are now hidden by default.
A "Show X Hidden Zero Rows" button appears in each view's toolbar
to reveal them. Applies to PM Edit, FA Workbook, and Expense Report.
Totals always include all rows regardless of visibility.

