From a53c6f93555fd859d6f2031ce3dc7f2aeed61549 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jacob Sirotkin <jake.sirotkin@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Mar 2026 06:20:24 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat: inline GL drill-down, reclass, formula UX, visual
 consistency

Phase 1: Zero-row hiding with toggle button (PM Edit, FA Workbook, Expense Report)
Phase 2: Inline GL expense drill-down with reclass in PM Edit and FA Workbook
  - Click description to expand invoices inline
  - Reclass via inline dropdown (no modal)
  - Undo reclass with one click
Phase 3: Visual consistency and formula UX
  - Expense report header now blue (was purple)
  - PM Edit computed cells (Estimate, Forecast, Proposed) show formula on click
  - fx badges on column headers for computed columns

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
